abstract: The software maker NetSuite and its investors sold an additional 930,000 shares. The stock, which had risen 49 percent since going public Dec. 20, fell back 6.6 percent.

lead_paragraph: The software maker NetSuite and its investors have sold an additional 930,000 shares. The stock, which had risen 49 percent since going public Dec. 20, fell 6.6 percent on Wednesday.
